<html>
<head>
	<title></title>
</head>
<body style="height: auto; min-height: auto;">
<div style="min-width:100%!important;max-width:100%!important;width:100%!important;margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f0f0f0">
<center style="background-color:#f0f0f0;margin:0;padding:0;max-width:100%!important;width:100%!important;min-width:100%!important">
<table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:600px;max-width:600px;min-width:600px;margin:0;padding:0" width="625">
	
		<tr>
			<td style="padding-bottom:0px;background-color:#f0f0f0" valign="top">
			<table bgcolor="#FFFFFF" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
				
					<tr>
						<td align="left" style="padding:50px 50px;margin:0;color:#333;line-height:1.1;font-family:'Arial Black';font-size:34px;text-align:left" valign="top">FOLLOWING UP ON YOUR LIVE CHAT</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td align="left" style="padding:0 50px 50px 50px;margin:0;text-align:left;font-family:'Arial';font-size:15px;color:#333;line-height:150%" valign="top">
						<p style="font-family:'Arial';font-weight: bold;font-size:18px;color:#000000">Dear {{{Recipient.Name}}},</p>

						<p style="font-family:'Arial';font-size:16px;color:#000000">Thank you for using our Live Chat Support channel. A case has been created on your behalf to track your request:</p>

						<ul style="font-family:'Arial';font-size:16px;color:#000000;margin-left:25px;list-style-type: none;">
							<li>Case Number: <strong>{{{Case.CaseNumber}}}</strong></li>
							<li>Opened on: <strong>{{{Case.CreatedDate}}}</strong></li>
							<li>Subject: <strong>{{{Case.Subject}}}</strong></li>
							<li>Chat transcript:<br />
							<strong>{{{Case.Case_Comment__c}}}</strong></li>
						</ul>

						<p style="font-family:'Arial';font-size:16px;color:#000000">If you require further assistance, {{{Case.OwnerFullName}}} will get back to you as soon as possible.</p>

						<p style="font-family:'Arial';font-size:16px;color:#000000">Otherwise, you can refer back to this case via our <a href="https://supportportal.brightcove.com/" style="color:#000000">Support Portal</a>.</p>

						<p style="font-family:'Arial';font-size:16px;color:#000000">Best regards,<br />
						<strong>The Brightcove Technical Support Team</strong></p>

						<p style="font-family:'Arial';font-size:15px;color:#000000">You can see all of your cases in our <a href="https://supportportal.brightcove.com/" style="color:#000000">Support Portal</a>, and current system status is always available on our <a href="https://status.brightcove.com/" style="color:#000000">Status Page</a>.<br />
						<br />
						{{{Case.E2CP__Case_Thread_Id__c}}}</p>
						</td>
					</tr>
				
			</table>
			</td>
		</tr>
	
</table>
</center>
</div>
</body>
</html>